title: Harnam Khera
text:
Harnam Khera is a village in <a href="Asoha">Asoha</a> block of <a href="Unnao%20district">Unnao district</a>, <a href="Uttar%20Pradesh">Uttar Pradesh</a>, <a href="India">India</a>. It has no schools and no healthcare facilities. As of 2011, its population is 347, in 81 households.
The <a href="1961%20Census%20of%20India">1961 census</a> recorded Harnam Khera as comprising 2 hamlets, with a total population of 203 (90 male and 113 female), in 41 households and 32 physical houses. The area of the village was given as 640 <a href="acre">acre</a>s.
